
 /**
 * SANGOCAST STORAGE ADAPTER v2.0
 * Multi‑environment storage with a consistent Promise‑based API.
 * Supports: Browser (IndexedDB / localStorage), Node.js (file system), In‑Memory fallback.
 *
 * Improvements:
 * - Real Node.js adapter using fs
 * - All adapters store strings only → uniform data handling
 * - IndexedDB race condition fixed, version upgrade support
 * - Proper error handling (no unhandled rejections)
 * - keys() method to list stored keys
 * - clearAll() works for all adapters
 * - Configurable adapter selection and prefix
 * - TypeScript‑ready JSDoc comments
 */

(function (global, factory) {
